Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Vomit)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby and Yang:WHOAAAAAA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yang: The view from Vale’s caught nothing on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby:Oh sis, that kid’s got a collapsable staff! 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oooh she’s got a fire sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby:Oow…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.53,0:01:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yang: Easy there, little sister…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re just weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.80,0:01:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby: JUST WEAPONS? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.03,0:01:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re an extension of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.61,0:01:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are a part of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.75,0:01:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OOOH they’re so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.70,0:01:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yang: Well, why can’t you swoon over your own weapon? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren’t you happy with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby: Of COURSE I am happy with Crescent Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.69,0:01:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just really like seeing new ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s like meeting new people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but better
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yang: Ruby, come ON. Why don’t you go try and make some friends of your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby: But why would I need friends when I have you?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yang: Well….Actually my friends are here now and I have to …
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby: Wait! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we supposed to go to our dorms? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are our dorms?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.52,0:01:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we have dorms? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah…I don’t know what I am doing…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weiss: What are you doing! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby: Ah.Sorry..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.69,0:02:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weiss: SORRY? Do you have any Idea of the damage you could’ve caused? 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.23,0:02:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby:Uhhh…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weiss: Gimme that! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is dust! Mined and purified from the Schnee Quarry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby: Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weiss:What are you? Brain dead? 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dust! Fire! Water! Lightning! Energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… Are you even listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.34,0:02:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is ANY of this sinking in? 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.06,0:02:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have to say for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby: Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weiss: Unbelievable! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exactly the kind of thing I was talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby: I’m really…REALLY sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weiss: Ugh! You complete dolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you even doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren’t you a little young to be attending beacon? 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.11,0:02:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby: Well…I….uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weiss: This isn’t your ordinary combat school
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it’s not just sparring and practicing, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re here to fight monsters so
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.05,0:02:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,watch where you’re going!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:02:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby: Hey, I said I was sorry, princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blake: It’s heiress, actually. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weiss Schnee
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,heiress to the Schnee Dust Company \N one of the largest producers of the energy propellant in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weiss: Finally, some recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.34,0:03:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blake: The same company infamous for its controversial labor forces and questionable business partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weiss: Wha…How dare….The nerve of…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Ruby:Creepy laugh)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.69,0:03:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby: I promise I will make this up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HAmm...
