Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby: Do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jaune: They will
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they will
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom always says that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,never mind
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby: Ehehehe
