Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jaune: Whoa! Is that a scythe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby: It’s also a customizable, high impact sniper rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Janue: A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby: It’s also a gun.
