Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jaune:Oh Uh
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got this sword? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby:Ooooo
