Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby: But…wouldn’t they weigh the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jaune: Yea….it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby: Well…..I’m kind of a dork when it comes to weapons.
