Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jaune: It’s a hand-me-down
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My great great grandfather used it to fight in a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruby: Sounds more like a family heirloom to me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not many people have an appreciation of the classics these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jaune: Yea…the classics.
